'''陰部神經'''（{{lang-en|pudendal nerve}}）為[[會陰|會陰部]]的主要[[神經|神經]]<ref name=Grant2013>{{cite book|last=AMR Agur, AF Dalley, JCB Grant|title=Grant's atlas of anatomy|year=2013|publisher=Wolters Kluwer Health/Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Philadelphia|isbn=978-1-60831-756-1|url=https://books.google.com/?id=SmflHHbed4EC&pg=PA274&dq=%22pudendal+nerve%22#v=onepage&q=%22pudendal%20nerve%22&f=false|edition=13th}}</ref>{{rp|274}}。在感覺方面，該神經負責傳送男性及女性[[外陰部|外陰部]]、[[肛門|肛門]]周圍，以及會陰的感覺信息；運動信息方面，則支配了{{le|男性尿道括約肌|External sphincter muscle of male urethra|男性}}及{{le|女性尿道括約肌|External sphincter muscle of female urethra|女性的尿道括約肌}}，和{{le|外肛門括約肌|external anal sphincter}}。一旦損傷則可能導致[[排糞失禁|排糞失禁]]，這類損傷常見於分娩後遺症，麻醉也可能造成類似的症狀。

陰部神經會經過{{le|閉孔內肌|obturator internus}}上的{{le|陰部管|pudendal canal}}。1836年，愛爾蘭解剖學家{{le|本傑明·阿爾科克|Benjamin Alcock}}首次描述陰部管，故該管又稱阿爾科克氏管（{{lang-en|Alcock's canal}}）。

==解剖==
[[File:Gray320.png|thumbnail]]

陰部神經共有一對，分別在身體的左右側。每一邊的神經都是由三根神經在{{le|骶棘韧带|sacrotuberous ligament}}及{{le|尾骨肌|coccygeus muscle}}的上邊界上方合成一根神經<ref name=Grays />。這三根神經中，中間的及下方的神經合成下方的神经索，因此變成二條神经索，再在骶棘韧带附近聯合成一條陰部神經<ref name=Shafik1995>{{cite journal|last=Shafik|first=A|author2=el-Sherif, M |author3=Youssef, A |author4= Olfat, ES |title=Surgical anatomy of the pudendal nerve and its clinical implications|journal=Clinical Anatomy|year=1995|volume=8|issue=2|pages=110–5|pmid=7712320 |doi=10.1002/ca.980080205}}</ref>。這三條神經源自第2、3、4對[[脊神經|骶部脊神經]]的{{le|腹支|Anterior ramus of spinal nerve}}，主要是來自第4對骶部脊神經<ref name=Grays>{{cite book|last=Standring S (editor in chief)|title=Gray's Anatomy: The Anatomical Basis of Clinical Practice|year=2004|publisher=Elsevier|isbn=978-0-443-06676-4|edition=39th}}</ref><ref name=Moore215>{{cite book|last=Moore|first=Keith L. Moore, Anne M.R. Agur ; in collaboration with and with content provided by Arthur F. Dalley II ; with the expertise of medical illustrator Valerie Oxorn and the developmental assistance of Marion E.|title=Essential clinical anatomy|year=2007|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Baltimore, MD|isbn=978-0-7817-6274-8|edition=3rd}}</ref>{{rp|215}}<ref name=Russell2006>{{cite book|last=Russell RM|title=Examination of peripheral nerve injuries an anatomical approach|year=2006|publisher=Thieme|location=Stuttgart|isbn=978-3-13-143071-7|url=https://books.google.com/?id=_NxeENi2lVAC&pg=PA157&dq=%22pudendal+nerve%22#v=onepage&q=%22pudendal%20nerve%22&f=false}}</ref>{{rp|157}}。

陰部神經通過{{le|梨狀肌|piriformis muscle}}及[[尾骨|尾骨]]之間的部位，從{{le|坐骨大孔|greater sciatic foramen}}的下方離開骨盆<ref name=Grays />。陰部神經通過骶棘韧带的外側，從{{le|坐骨小孔| lesser sciatic foramen}}再進入骨盆，之後會伴隨著[[陰部內動脈|陰部內動脈]]及{{le|陰部內靜脈|internal pudendal vein}}，沿著{{le|坐骨直腸窩|Ischioanal fossa}}的側壁往上往前，和內動脈和內靜脈包覆在{{le|閉孔肌筋膜| obturator fascia}}的鞘中，稱為{{le|阴部管|pudendal canal}}<ref name=ASCRStextbook />{{rp|8}}。

陰部神經在陰部管內會分支，先分支為{{le|內直腸神經|inferior anal nerve}}，之後是[[會陰神經|會陰神經]]，最後是男性的{{le|陰莖背神經|dorsal nerve of the penis}}或是女性的{{le|陰蒂背神經|Dorsal nerve of the clitoris|陰蒂的背神經}}<ref name=ASCRStextbook />{{rp|34}}。

===神經核===
此神經是{{le|骶叢|Sacral plexus}}的主要分支之一<ref name=Brucker2013>{{cite book|author1=TL King |author2=MC Brucker |author3=JM Kriebs |author4=JO Fahey |title=Varney's midwifery|year=2013|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|isbn=978-1-284-02542-2|url=https://books.google.com/?id=dbaNAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA950&dq=%22pudendal+nerve%22#v=onepage&q=%22pudendal%20nerve%22&f=false|edition=Fifth}}</ref>{{rp|950}}，神經纖維起源自[[骶骨|骶骨]]段[[脊髓|脊髓]]的{{le|歐氏神經核|Onuf's nucleus}}<ref name=Shafik1995 />。

===變異===
陰部神經源自的神經位置也可能會變化，例如有些人的陰部神經可能是源自{{le|坐骨神經|Sciatic nerve}}<ref>{{cite journal|last=Nayak|first=Soubhagya R.|author2=Madhan Kumar, S.J.; Krishnamurthy, Ashwin; Latha Prabhu, V.; D'costa, Sujatha; Jetti, Raghu|title=Unusual origin of dorsal nerve of penis and abnormal formation of pudendal nerve—Clinical significance|journal=Annals of Anatomy - Anatomischer Anzeiger|date=November 2006|volume=188|issue=6|pages=565–566|doi=10.1016/j.aanat.2006.06.011}}</ref>。，因此坐骨神經的損傷也會影響陰部神經。有時第1節骶神經的後支也可能發展成為陰部神經，甚至是更少見的第5節骶神經（S5）<ref name=Shafik1995>{{cite journal|last=Shafik|first=A|author2=el-Sherif, M |author3=Youssef, A |author4= Olfat, ES |title=Surgical anatomy of the pudendal nerve and its clinical implications|journal=Clinical Anatomy|year=1995|volume=8|issue=2|pages=110–5|pmid=7712320 |doi=10.1002/ca.980080205}}</ref>。

==功能==
陰部神經同時具有運動及感覺兩種功能，在自律神經系統方面僅有交感神經的神經纖維，沒有[[副交感神經|副交感神經]]的纖維<ref>{{cite book|last=Neill|first=editor-in-chief, Jimmy D.|title=Knobil and Neill's physiology of reproduction|year=2006|publisher=Elsevier|location=Amsterdam|isbn=0-12-515400-3|edition=3rd}}</ref>{{rp|1738}}。

男性的陰部神經會分出{{le|陰莖背神經|dorsal nerve of penis}}支配[[陰莖|陰莖]]的感覺，女性則會分出{{le|陰蒂背神經|dorsal nerve of clitoris}}支配[[陰蒂|陰蒂]]感覺<ref name=GRAYS2005 />{{rp|422}}。男性的[[陰囊|陰囊]]後側由{{le|陰囊後神經|Posterior scrotal nerves}}支配其感覺，女性對應的{{le|陰唇後神經|Posterior labial nerves}}會支配[[陰唇|陰唇]]的感覺。這些部位有許多神經傳導其感覺，陰部神經即為其中之一<ref name=ORT2007>{{cite book|last=Ort|first=Bruce Ian Bogart, Victoria|title=Elsevier's integrated anatomy and embryology|url=https://archive.org/details/elseviersintegra0000boga|year=2007|publisher=Elsevier Saunders|location=Philadelphia, Pa.|isbn=978-1-4160-3165-9}}</ref>。陰部神經也傳導{{le|肛管|anal canal}}部位的感覺<ref name=ASCRStextbook />{{rp|8}}。陰部神經會傳導陰莖及陰蒂的感覺，因此也是在陰莖[[勃起|勃起]]及[[陰蒂勃起|陰蒂勃起]]過程中的传入神经<ref>{{cite book|last=Babayan|first=Mike B. Siroky, Robert D. Oates, Richard K.|title=Handbook of urology diagnosis and therapy|year=2004|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Philadelphia, PA|isbn=978-0-7817-4221-4|edition=3rd}}</ref> {{rp|147}}。陰部神經也負責[[射精|射精]]相關的功能<ref>{{cite book |last=Penson|first= David F.|title=Male Sexual Function: A Guide to Clinical Management|year=2002|publisher=Annals of Internal Medicine}}</ref>。

陰部神經的分支也支配[[會陰|會陰]]及{{le|骨盆底|Pelvic floor}}的肌肉，包含{{le|球海绵体肌|Bulbospongiosus muscle}}、{{le|坐骨海绵体肌|Ischiocavernosus muscle}}<ref name=ORT2007 />，以及{{le|提肛肌|Levator ani}}（包括腸骨尾骨肌、{{le|恥骨尾骨肌|Pubococcygeus muscle}}、{{le|耻骨直肠肌|puborectalis}}、女性的恥骨陰道肌或是男性的前列腺提肌）<ref name=GRAYS2005 />{{rp|422}}<ref>{{cite journal|last=Guaderrama|first=Noelani M.|author2=Liu, Jianmin |author3=Nager, Charles W. |author4=Pretorius, Dolores H. |author5=Sheean, Geoff |author6=Kassab, Ghada |author7= Mittal, Ravinder K. |title=Evidence for the Innervation of Pelvic Floor Muscles by the Pudendal Nerve|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_obstetrics-and-gynecology_2005-10_106_4/page/774|journal=Obstetrics & Gynecology|date=October 2005|volume=106|issue=4|pages=774–781|doi=10.1097/01.AOG.0000175165.46481.a8}}</ref>、{{le|外肛門括約肌|External anal sphincter}}（透過下肛門分支）<ref name=ASCRStextbook>{{cite book|editors=Wolff BG et al.|title=The ASCRS textbook of colon and rectal surgery|url=https://archive.org/details/ascrstextbookofc0000unse|year=2007|publisher=Springer|location=New York|isbn=0-387-24846-3}}</ref>{{rp|7}}、以及{{le|男性尿道外括約肌|External sphincter muscle of male urethra}}或{{le|女性尿道外括約肌|External sphincter muscle of female urethra}}<ref name=GRAYS2005>{{cite book|last=Drake|first=Richard L.|title=Gray's anatomy for students|year=2005|publisher=Elsevier/Churchill Livingstone|location=Philadelphia|isbn=978-0-8089-2306-0|author2=Vogl, Wayne |author3=Tibbitts, Adam W.M. Mitchell  |author4=illustrations by Richard |author5= Richardson, Paul }}</ref>{{rp|424–425}}。

陰部神經還透過[[乙醯膽鹼|乙醯膽鹼]]釋放控制{{le|尿道外括約肌|external urethral sphincter}}的肌張力。當乙醯膽鹼的釋放量增加，尿道外括約肌內的骨骼肌纖維會收縮，使尿液留在膀胱，反之則能促進排尿<ref>{{cite journal | pmc = 2897743 | pmid=18490916 | doi=10.1038/nrn2401 | volume=9 | title=The neural control of micturition | date=June 2008 | journal=Nat. Rev. Neurosci. | pages=453–66 | last1 = Fowler | first1 = CJ | last2 = Griffiths | first2 = D | last3 = de Groat | first3 = WC}}</ref>。

==臨床意義==
===麻醉===
{{le|陰部麻醉|Pudendal anesthesia}}也稱為阴部神经阻斷，或鞍神经阻斷（saddle nerve block），是產科使用的[[局部麻醉|局部麻醉]]，可在[[分娩|分娩]]時麻醉陰部<ref>{{cite book|title=Maternal, Neonatal, and Women's Health Nursing, Volume 1|author1=Lynna Y. Littleton |author2=Joan Engebretson |publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2002|page=727}}</ref>。此麻醉方式會在陰道內壁注射[[利多卡因|利多卡因]]，目的是要影響陰部神經<ref>{{cite web |last1=Satpathy |first1=Hemant K. |last2=Fleming |first2=Alfred D. |last3=Fossen |first3=Katie A. |last4=Frey |first4=Donald R. |last5=Macario |first5=Alex |displayauthors=1 |editor1-last=Isaacs |editor1-first=Christine |editor2-last=Windle |editor2-first=Mary L. |displayeditors=1 |title=Transvaginal Pudendal Nerve Block |url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/83078-overview |publisher=WebMD LLC |accessdate=2015-07-19 |archive-date=2019-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728153232/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/83078-overview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===損傷===
<!-- Causes of dysfunction -->
陰部神經可能會被壓縮或是伸展，造成暫時或是永久的[[神经病_(神经系统疾病)|神經病變]]。若陰部神經拉伸了原來長度的12%，可能會造成不可逆的神經受損<ref name=ASCRStextbook />{{rp|655}}。若盆腔底急性過度拉伸（例如滯產或是難產）或慢性過度拉伸（因[[便秘|便秘]]造成[[排便|排便]]時的慢性拉伸），可能會讓陰部神經出現拉伸造成的神經病變<ref name=ASCRStextbook />。{{le|陰部神經卡壓|Pudendal nerve entrapment}}也稱為阿爾科克氏管症候群（Alcock canal syndrome），是非常少見的疾病，多半發生在職業的[[自行车运动|自行車選手]]身上<ref>{{cite journal |author=Mellion MB |title=Common cycling injuries. Management and prevention |journal=Sports Med |volume=11 |issue=1 |pages=52–70 |date=January 1991 |pmid=2011683 |doi= 10.2165/00007256-199111010-00004|url=}}</ref>。像[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]及[[多发性硬化症|多发性硬化症]]等系統性疾病也可能透過{{le|脫髓鞘病|Demyelinating disease}}或是其他機制使陰部神經受損<ref name=ASCRStextbook />{{rp|37}}。骨盆腔的腫瘤（最著名的是大型的{{le|骶尾部畸胎瘤|Sacrococcygeal teratoma}}）或是去除腫瘤的手術都可能造成神經永久的受損<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Lim|first1=Jit F.|last2=Tjandra|first2=Joe J.|last3=Hiscock|first3=Richard|last4=Chao|first4=Michael W. T.|last5=Gibbs|first5=Peter|title=Preoperative Chemoradiation for Rectal Cancer Causes Prolonged Pudendal Nerve Terminal Motor Latency|journal=Diseases of the Colon & Rectum|volume=49|issue=1|pages=12–19|doi=10.1007/s10350-005-0221-7}}</ref>。

<!-- Signs and symptoms of dysfunction -->
若單側的陰部神經病變可能會造成[[大便失禁|大便失禁]]，但也有例外<!--，This is because crossover innervation of the external anal sphincter occurs in some individuals---><ref name="ASCRStextbook" />{{rp|34}}。

===影像===
用一般的[[X射线计算机断层成像|斷層掃描]]或是[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]，很難對陰部神經顯像。不過透過斷層掃描的引導，可以將針插到鄰近陰部{{le|神經血管束|Neurovascular bundle}}的部位。{{le|坐骨棘|schial spine}}在斷層掃描時很容易識別，因此會插在此一部位。脊椎針會通過{{le|臀肌|Gluteal muscles}}前進，在坐骨棘上前進幾個毫米。之後會注射X光的顯影劑，讓阴部管內的神經更加清楚，也可以確認針插入的位置是否正確。然後會注射[[可的松|可的松]]到神經中，進行局部麻醉進行確認，也治療外陰部的慢性疼痛（女性稱為[[外阴疼痛|外阴疼痛]]）、骨盆疼痛和肛門直腸疼痛等<ref>{{cite journal |author=Calvillo O, Skaribas IM, Rockett C. |title=Computed tomography-guided pudendal nerve block. A new diagnostic approach to long-term anoperineal pain: a report of two cases |journal=Reg Anesth Pain Med |volume= 25|issue=4 |pages=420–3 |year=2000 |pmid=10925942 |url= |doi=10.1053/rapm.2000.7620|last2=Skaribas |last3=Rockett }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Hough DM, Wittenberg KH, Pawlina W, Maus TP, King BF, Vrtiska TJ, Farrell MA, Antolak SJ Jr. |title=Chronic perineal pain caused by pudendal nerve entrapment: anatomy and CT-guided perineural injection technique |journal=Am J Roentgenol |volume=181 |issue=2 |pages=561–7 |year=2003 |pmid=12876048 |url= |doi=10.2214/ajr.181.2.1810561|last2=Wittenberg |last3=Pawlina |last4=Maus |last5=King |last6=Vrtiska |last7=Farrell |last8=Antolak Jr }}</ref>。
====神經傳導潛伏期試驗====
陰部神經的延遲時間可以量化，具體的定義是從在感覺神經給電刺激的時間起，到運動神經有訊號使陰部肌肉收縮的時間，時間太長代表神經受損<ref name=Santoro2010>{{cite book|last=G.A. Santoro, A.P. Wieczorek, C.I. Bartram (editors)|title=Pelvic floor disorders imaging and multidisciplinary approach to management|year=2010|publisher=Springer|location=Dordrecht|isbn=978-88-470-1542-5}}</ref>{{rp|46}}。測試時會有兩個固定在手指端的刺激電極及兩個量測電極（St Mark電極）<ref name=Santoro2010 />{{rp|46}}。

==歷史==
陰部神經的拉丁文為「''{{lang|la|Nervus pudendus}}''」。「''{{lang|la|Nervus}}''」一詞指的是神經；「''{{lang|la|Pudenda}}''」一詞來自[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]，意即外生殖器官，乃源自「''{{lang|la|pudendum}}''」這個字，意思是「帶來羞恥的部份」<ref>{{cite web|last=Harper|first=Douglas|title=Pudendum|url=http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?term=pudendum&allowed_in_frame=0|work=Online Etymology Dictionary|accessdate=2014-02-28|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118230754/http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?term=pudendum&allowed_in_frame=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|陰部管|pudendal canal}}也稱為阿尔科克氏管（Alcock's canal），得名自1836年首次紀錄此一部位的愛爾蘭解剖學家{{le|班傑明·阿爾科克|Benjamin Alcock}}。阿爾科克在{{le|羅伯特·本特利·托德|Robert Bentley Todd}}的《生理暨解剖學百科全書》（''The Cyclopædia of Anatomy and Physiology''） 一書中，於描述{{le|髂動脈群|Iliac artery}}的章節內首次提及陰部神經及陰部管<ref>{{cite journal|last=Oelhafen|first=Kim|author2=Shayota, Brian J. |author3=Muhleman, Mitchel |author4=Klaassen, Zachary |author5=Tubbs, R. Shane |author6= Loukas, Marios |title=Benjamin Alcock (1801-?) and his canal|journal=Clinical Anatomy|date=2013-09|volume=26|issue=6|pages=662–666|doi=10.1002/ca.22080|pmid=22488487}}</ref>。

